name: THE SEED
description: "The Seed" is a chilling, paranoid tale that will make you literally question your sanity! A sequential symphony of eye-popping Lovecraftian Jazz! 54 pages of TERROR plus 16 pages of extras for just 99 cents! Download right to your favourite reading device or computer- IF YOU DARE!

name: CIRCUS DAY
description:
Step Right Up! Step Right Up! CIRCUS DAY is the comic that will CHANGE YOUR LIFE! 26 incredible pages of story, PLUS 18 never-before-seen pages of extras (peek behind the curtain for no added price!). You can't find a better deal! 
Delivered to the computer or digital device of your choosing as a beautiful PDF file for the insanely low price of 99 cents!

name: Convention Sketchbook 2011
description:
This Convention sketchbook is packed with goodness that will blow your comic book-lovin' mind! It contains two sections: PINUPS; displaying some of your favorite characters from comics and elsewhere (Superman, Thor, Wonder Woman, Conan, Dracula, etc.). And part two is TOMFOOLERY; where we poke fun at your favorite superheroes.
22 pages of full-color art.
Supplies are limited! Order now.

Please allow 1-2 weeks for shipping.
Cost includes shipping and handling.
